test-results/playwright-report/
test-results/playwright-artifacts/
test-results/.last-run.json

# >>> autothing >>>
# Evidence binaries + run liveness state (unversioned; sha256 in evidence-index).
# Resume-critical small files (FLOW_PLAN.md, evidence-index.json, gate-status.json,
# RUN_LOG.md, RUN_SPEC.md, LANDING.md) stay VERSIONED — never ignore the runs dir.
docs/autothing/runs/**/*.cast
docs/autothing/runs/**/*.webm
docs/autothing/runs/**/*.mp4
docs/autothing/runs/**/*.png
docs/autothing/runs/**/status.json
docs/autothing/runs/**/owner.lock.json
